products.name: Genrui Fully Auto Chemistry Analyzer GS300 Plus
products.description: GS300 Plus is one of the best bench-top chemistry analyzers, which is flexible for small to medium-sized laboratories.

products.name: Mindray BS-240 Fully Automated Chemistry Analyzer
products.description: BS-240 is a “CUTE”, multi-functional benchtop chemistry analyzer with a throughput of 200 tests per hour.

products.name: Erba XL-180 Full Automated Chemistry Analyzer
products.description: XL 180 is a fully automated, random access, and discrete clinical chemistry analyzer with a throughput of 180 tests per hour with minimal water consumption.

products.name: Erba XL-200 Full Automated Chemistry Analyzer
products.description: XL 200 is a fully automated, random access and discrete clinical chemistry analyzer that enhances productivity and turnaround time.

products.name: Erba XL-640 Full Automated Chemistry Analyzer
products.description: XL 640 is a fully automated biochemistry analyzer with a throughput of 640 tests per hour.

products.name: Erba XL-1000 Full Automated Chemistry Analyzer
products.description: XL 1000 with a throughput of up to 1040 tests per hour is the ideal instrument for centralizing the complete biochemistry testing load on a single fully automated platform. Increased walk-away productivity and less human intervention make it an ideal analyzer for large laboratories.

products.name: Genrui Fully Auto Chemistry Analyzer GS480A
products.description: The GS480A is a robust and fully-auto chemistry analyzer.

products.name: Genrui WP-21A Semi-Automated Systems
products.description: Genrui WP21A is a NEW generation semi-auto chemistry analyzer, it is one of the best models in the same series.

products.name: Mindray BA-88A Semi-Automated Systems
products.description: A semi-automatic chemistry analyzer with a large touch-screen and easy-to-use operation software.
